OL,3,C'No patient will be left without care'
OL,4,Cafter hospice cuts
OL,6,F'No patient will be left without end
OL,7,Fof life care' following cuts and
OL,8,Fredundancies at the island's only
OL,9,Fhospice, the Health Minister on the
OL,10,FIsle of Man says.
OL,12,FClaire Christian MHK gave an urgent
OL,13,Fstatement during a sitting of the
OL,14,FHouse of Keys in the Island's
OL,15,Fparliament.
OL,17,FHospice Isle of Man announced
OL,18,Fredundancies and changes to its
OL,19,Fservices on 26 March, as it says its
OL,20,F"financial reality is increasingly
OL,21,Funstable".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
