OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775049066
OL,3,C'No patient will be left without care'
OL,4,Cafter hospice cuts
OL,6,FMs Christian said she was unable to
OL,7,Fsay how services will be impacted
OL,8,Funtil a three-week voluntary
OL,9,Fredundancy process has been completed
OL,10,Fby the hospice.
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
